OL,3,CTech firms and bosses face large fines
OL,4,Cfor failing to remove knife crime
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FTech companies and individual
OL,8,Fexecutives face being collectively
OL,9,Ffined up to #70,000 each time a post
OL,10,Frelating to knife crime is not removed
OL,11,Ffor their sites.
OL,13,FThe Government has expanded a
OL,14,Fpreviously announced plan to fine
OL,15,Findividual tech bosses #10,000 when
OL,16,Ftheir platform fails to remove content
OL,17,Flinked to knife crime, and will now
OL,18,Fissue additional fines of up to
OL,19,F#60,000 to a company itself each time
OL,20,Fit fails to remove individual posts.
