OL,3,CTech firms and bosses face large fines
OL,4,Cfor failing to remove knife crime
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FThe Home Office said the sanctions are
OL,8,Fpart of plans to combat content that
OL,9,Fadvertises illegal knives and other
OL,10,Foffensive weapons to young people, as
OL,11,Fwell as glorifying or inciting
OL,12,Fviolence.
OL,14,FThe laws will also make a greater
OL,15,Frange of platforms liable, including
OL,16,Fsearch engines, social media platforms
OL,17,Fand online marketplaces, with the aim
OL,18,Fof capturing all online providers
OL,19,Fwhich might currently be failing to
OL,20,Fremove content.
