OL,3,CTech firms and bosses face large fines
OL,4,Cfor failing to remove knife crime
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FThey will be introduced in an
OL,8,Famendment to the Crime and Policing
OL,9,FBill.
OL,11,FCrime and policing minister Dame Diana
OL,12,FJohnson said: "The kind of content
OL,13,Fthat young people scroll through every
OL,14,Fday online is sickening and I will not
OL,15,Faccept any notion that restricting
OL,16,Faccess to this harmful material is too
OL,17,Fdifficult.
