OL,3,CTech firms and bosses face large fines
OL,4,Cfor failing to remove knife crime
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,F"Our children need more from us. That
OL,8,Fis why we are now going further than
OL,9,Fever to hold to account the tech
OL,10,Fcompanies who are not doing enough to
OL,11,Fsafeguard young people from content
OL,12,Fwhich incites violence, particularly
OL,13,Fin young boys.
OL,15,F"Curbing the impact of this kind of
OL,16,Fcontent will be key for our mission to
OL,17,Fhalve knife crime, but more widely our
OL,18,FPlan for Change across Government to
OL,19,Fdo more protect young people from
OL,20,Fdamaging and dangerous content."
