OL,3,CTech firms and bosses face large fines
OL,4,Cfor failing to remove knife crime
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FThe development comes after Ofcom
OL,8,Fannounced the final version of its
OL,9,Fcodes of practice under the Online
OL,10,FSafety Act aimed at protecting
OL,11,Fchildren from online harm.
OL,13,FPatrick Green, chief executive of
OL,14,Fknife crime prevention charity the Ben
OL,15,FKinsella Trust, said: "The portrayal
OL,16,Fof knife crime on social media has
OL,17,Fsignificantly hindered efforts to
OL,18,Freduce it.
OL,26,@wD@WOU
