OL,3,CTech firms and bosses face large fines
OL,4,Cfor failing to remove knife crime
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,F"Beyond merely normalising,
OL,8,Fglamorising, and desensitising young
OL,9,Fpeople to violence, it has often
OL,10,Fprovided an illegal avenue for
OL,11,Fpurchasing knives without adequate
OL,12,Fsafeguards, such as proper age
OL,13,Fverification.
OL,15,F"Social media companies and their
OL,16,Fexecutives have repeatedly failed to
OL,17,Faddress these issues.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
