OL,3,CTech firms and bosses face large fines
OL,4,Cfor failing to remove knife crime
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,F"Therefore, I welcome today's
OL,8,Fannouncement from the Government to
OL,9,Ftake decisive action and hold these
OL,10,Fexecutives accountable.
OL,12,F"I also thank the Government for
OL,13,Flistening to the Coalition to Tackle
OL,14,FKnife Crime and for extending these
OL,15,Fsanctions to include social media
OL,16,Fcompanies, who have a responsibility
OL,17,Fto keep young people safe on their
OL,18,Fplatforms."
